       &lt;inlinetext&gt;construct a gateway and footpath in the
              &lt;inlinedefterm&gt;Churchyard&lt;/inlinedefterm&gt; of the Parish Church 
              (the &lt;inlinedefterm istermbeingdefined="true"&gt;Works&lt;/inlinedefterm&gt;)&lt;/inlinetext&gt;
    &lt;/inlinedefdesc&gt;
 &lt;/inlinedefitem&gt;
&lt;/text&gt;
 
